OL,3,CCould Donald Trump win a $5bn lawsuit
OL,4,Cagainst the BBC?
OL,6,FDonald Trump has followed through on
OL,7,Fhis threat to sue the BBC over an
OL,8,Fedited speech despite the
OL,9,Fcorporation's apology.
OL,11,FAlthough the BBC apologised and
OL,12,Fretracted the episode, it refused to
OL,13,Fcompensate Trump, who claims the
OL,14,Fedited version of a 2021 speech
OL,15,Fbroadcast by Panorama caused him major
OL,16,Ffinancial and reputational harm. He
OL,17,Fintends to seek $1`5 billion in
OL,18,Fdamages.
