OL,3,CCould Donald Trump win a $5bn lawsuit
OL,4,Cagainst the BBC?
OL,6,FThe prospect of a multi-billion-pound
OL,7,Flawsuit is a daunting one for the BBC
OL,8,Fand the British government, but the
OL,9,Fpresident faces legal hurdles on both
OL,10,Fsides of the Atlantic.
OL,12,FWhy is Donald Trump suing?
OL,14,FThe dispute was sparked by an edition
OL,15,Fof the BBC's flagship current affairs
OL,16,Fseries Panorama, titled Trump: A
OL,17,FSecond Chance? broadcast days before
OL,18,Fthe 2024 US presidential election.
