OL,6,FThe third-party production company
OL,7,Fthat made the film spliced together
OL,8,Fthree quotes from two sections of the
OL,9,F2021 speech into what appeared to be
OL,10,Fone quote in which Trump urged
OL,11,Fsupporters to march with him and
OL,12,F"fight like hell".
OL,14,FTrump's demand that he be compensated
OL,15,Ffor "overwhelming financial and
OL,16,Freputational harm".
OL,18,FAmong the parts cut out was a section
OL,19,Fwhere Trump said he wanted supporters
OL,20,Fto demonstrate peacefully.
