OL,6,FChairman Samir Shah has sent a
OL,7,Fpersonal letter to the White House to
OL,8,Fapologise for the editing, and lawyers
OL,9,Ffor the corporation have written to
OL,10,Fthe president's legal team, strongly
OL,11,Fdisagreeing that there was a basis for
OL,12,Fa defamation claim.
OL,14,FThe broadcaster said it will not air
OL,15,Fthe Panorama episode Trump: A Second
OL,16,FChance? again, and published a
OL,17,Fretraction on the show's webpage on
OL,18,FThursday.
