OL,6,FTrump also said the lawsuit would
OL,7,F"probably" be filed "someplace in the
OL,8,FUS", but commented that litigation in
OL,9,Fthe UK "moves a little bit quickly".
OL,11,FHowever, deadlines to bring the case
OL,12,Fin English courts, where defamation
OL,13,Fdamages rarely exceed #100,000,
OL,14,Fexpired more than a year ago.
OL,16,FWhile Florida law has a two-year
OL,17,Flimit, bringing a defamation case in
OL,18,FAmerica will mean Trump faces a
OL,19,Ftougher legal standard.
