OL,3,CCould Donald Trump win a $5bn lawsuit
OL,4,Cagainst the BBC?
OL,6,FTrump would need to prove three major
OL,7,Fcomponents - that the content
OL,8,Fpublished was factually false in a
OL,9,Fdefamatory way; that he suffered harm
OL,10,Fdue to the false and defamatory
OL,11,Fcoverage; and that the media
OL,12,Forganisation knew it was false and
OL,13,Facted with "actual malice".
OL,15,FLegal experts say that the BBC could
OL,16,Fshow that Trump was not harmed because
OL,17,Fhe was ultimately elected president in
OL,18,F2024.
