OL,6,FIn July, Paramount, which owns CBS,
OL,7,Fagreed to pay $16 million to settle a
OL,8,Flawsuit filed by Trump over a 60
OL,9,FMinutes interview with former Vice
OL,10,FPresident Kamala Harris. Trump alleged
OL,11,Fthat the interview was edited to
OL,12,Fenhance how Harris, the Democratic
OL,13,Fnominee for president in 2024, sounded.
OL,15,FTrump told GB News in an interview on
OL,16,FFriday night: "I think that was worse
OL,17,Fthan the Kamala (Harris) thing with
OL,18,FCBS and 60 Minutes."
